Saturday June 21st at argos – from 11h00 till 18h00, Werfstraat 13 Rue du Chantier, 1000 Brussels Join us for a festive weekend at argos. Come for the books, the launch of a new publication by argos, a presentation of the a.pass publication IN THESE CIRCUMSTANCES or stay for the exhibition and screenings!
Presentation of the a.pass publication In These Circumstances (Saturday 16:00) by Philippine Hoegen (Ed.), Pia Louwerens, Túlio Rosa & Tamar Levit

